history.p: Nielsen composed the melody for Kolding Almenskole's May Festival in 1906. It was originally composed for three equal voices but was later re-arranged.

event.corpName: Girl's Choir from Borgerskolen on Christiansgade

event.desc: The song was sung by a choir of 1200 children.
